Class QuadPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • QuadPackage
  • public class QuadPackage
extends java.lang.Object
    QuadPackage object is used to communicate between QuadNodes. It carries the previous processed node and a inserted/removed point. If the point is null, it means no action is done.
    Version:
    2021-10-16
    Author:
    Ting-Jui Hsu
